          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"rock-paper-scissors-and-beyond\">Rock, Paper, Scissors ... and beyond?</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Rock-Paper-Scissors has <strong>3</strong> elements. Rock-Paper-Scissors-Lizard-Spock has <strong>5</strong>.\nCould we make a variant with <strong>4</strong>? Or <strong>6</strong>?</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">For a game to be <em>fair</em>, every element must beat the same number of others.\nWith <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(n||)</marimo-tex> elements, each must beat exactly <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(k = \\frac{n - 1}{2}||)</marimo-tex> others.\nThat's only a whole number when <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(n||)</marimo-tex> is <strong>odd</strong>.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Use the keyboard shortcuts to explore the widget. Click in the keyboard widget area and use the\narrows to see the widget update.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
